Package Prelims.Project2.LinkedListImplementation

Class DoublyLinkedList<E>

java.lang.Object
Prelims.Project2.LinkedListImplementation.DoublyLinkedList<E>
Type Parameters:
E - The type of elements to be stored in the linked list.
All Implemented Interfaces:
LinkedListInterface<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Course, Term
public class DoublyLinkedList<E> extends Object implements LinkedListInterface<E>
DoublyLinkedList is a generic class that implements a doubly-linked list data structure. It allows insertion, deletion, and retrieval of elements from both ends and at specific indices.
